Though the crik that flows thru Ohatchee is really much of nothing, to the proud people of Ohatchee, it's everything. I enjoyed the crik in Ohatchee very much. Swam. Fished. Frog Gigged. And throwed the football w Diddy.  Sometimes I catched the pass from Diddy. But when I missed the catch from Diddy's football passes, the ball landed in the crik and it got wet.
